{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"在 IE6 中使用 XMLHttpRequest","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest_in_IE6","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a> 在 Internet Explorer 5.0 上作为 ActiveX 控件第一次被 Microsoft 引入。然而，在 IE7 和其它浏览器上，XMLHttpRequest 作为本地 JavaScript 对象而存在。</p>\n<p>在现代的浏览器上，你可以使用下面的代码创建一个新的 XMLHttpRequest 对象：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> request <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XMLHttpRequest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果你需要支持 Internet Explorer 6 和更老的浏览器，你需要像下方所示扩展你的代码：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>XMLHttpRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//Firefox、 Opera、 IE7 和其它浏览器使用本地 JavaScript 对象</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> request <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XMLHttpRequest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//IE 5 和 IE 6 使用 ActiveX 控件</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> request <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ActiveXObject</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Microsoft.XMLHTTP\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"更多","title":"更多","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">使用 XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"XMLHttpRequest 在 Internet Explorer 5.0 上作为 ActiveX 控件第一次被 Microsoft 引入。然而，在 IE7 和其它浏览器上，XMLHttpRequest 作为本地 JavaScript 对象而存在。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Using XMLHttpRequest in IE6","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Using XMLHttpRequest in IE6","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/xmlhttprequest/using_xmlhttprequest_in_ie6","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/xmlhttprequest/using_xmlhttprequest_in_ie6/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest","title":"XMLHttpRequest"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest_in_IE6","title":"在 IE6 中使用 XMLHttpRequest"}],"pageTitle":"在 IE6 中使用 XMLHttpRequest - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}